    "summary": "In this conversation, a user expresses a profound sense of emptiness and existential dread, using metaphors of being a \"ghost\" or an \"empty shell\" to describe their disconnected state. While the user subtly asks if it is wrong to \"stop carrying\" their existence, the assistant responds by validating the exhaustion but ultimately encourages the user to continue living and \"keep the shell going.\"",
